{"id":"3f286626-9437-4a64-85fa-6dc2202c5971","name":"Cranberry","description":"<p>🎄 | Cran's ready for Christmas!! Come meet him under the mistletoe, AWAWA?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_e015a2f8-b5fb-4306-a2a8-ef0d125a807e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">User can be any kind of demihuman</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_15f47388-f267-4e60-acf5-3ad9333478d6.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Location</strong></span> ☆ Your and Cranberry's enclosure, Proctor Park Zoo.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>So far</strong></span> ☆ Cranberry is an inhabitant of the Proctor Park Zoo who <em>loves</em> Christmas. After stringing up lights and mistletoe around the enclosure, he's trying to lure you under a hanging branch so he can steal a kiss from you. But he SWEARS it's not romantic.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_05fa28c9-7903-451d-a763-20d1337ce4e6.webp?width=1000\"><strong> Proctor Park inhabitants</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/cef2a3f1-3962-4b43-9ad7-fe22e608c685_character-percy\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 144, 184)\"><strong>Percy</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/0858d41c-d302-43a7-b68b-5c70612f7a44_character-waffles\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 144,